Point Of Sales - Inventory Managemant Sysytem
Project Overview
Point Of sales is tracking sales that happens with Iventory That we manage.

Technologies Used
Backend: Node.js, Express, MongoDB, Mongoose
Frontend: React, React Router, Vite, React-BootStrap
Others: Axios
Installation Instructions
Backend Setup
Prerequisites for Backend Setup To set up and run the backend of your POS software, you need to ensure the following prerequisites are met:

Software Requirements
Node.js (v16 or higher): Node.js is the runtime environment for running JavaScript on the server-side. npm (Node Package Manager): npm is included with Node.js and is used to manage the project's dependencies. MongoDB: MongoDB is a NoSQL database used to store the book data. Git (optional, for cloning the repository): Git is used for version control and cloning the repository from a remote source.

Installation Instructions:
in Git Bash mkdir repo_name (creates a local repository) cd repo_name

backend
Here are the detailed steps to set up the backend of your  application: *In VSC terminal backend init Enter name of project-backend Enter Port Enter Mongo uri cd backend Run npm i Change mongo uri to your uri in .env file Run: npm run dev

Frontend Setup
Prerequisites: Ensure you have the following installed on your system:

Node.js (v16 or higher) npm (Node package manager, which comes with Node.js) Git (optional, if you're cloning from a repository)

Here are the detailed steps to set up the frontend of your Point of Sales application application:
Frontend Setup Instructions Create React in Vite

*In VSC terminal -npm create vite@latest -name project frontend -select framework react -select javascript -cd into frontend -npm install -npm run dev -ctrl & click into local host

Usage Instructions:
Ensure the backend server is running on the default port 5000. Open another terminal and ensure the frontend development server is running. Open your browser and navigate to http://localhost:5173 to view the application.

API Endpoints:  products, /editproduct?id=667b39efec66c65be4b8e197 ,deleteproduct/?productId=667a335acacafe3bdc0ee150 ,addproduct

/products :end point to GET Reqquest
/editproduct?id=667b39efec66c65be4b8e197 : PUT end point
/deleteproduct/?productId=667a335acacafe3bdc0ee150 :DELETE end point.
/addproduct : to CREATE end point
